The World Cup fever has definitely kicked in with teams touching down Russia already. It’s two days to the World Cup and there’s so much excitement in the air. Maybe, we are not stoked about the opening fixture between hosts Russia and Saudi Arabia, however, asides the potentially drab opening game, there’s loads to be excited about. Part of the thrill is derived from the jerseys different teams will wear at the World Cup. Here we rate just how good or bad are the jerseys of the African contingents at the World Cup in Russia. Tunisia  <img class="size-medium wp-image-658977 aligncenter lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/on-display-the-tunisia-shirt-for-the-fifa-world-cup-2018-in-russia-picture-id962496684-story-large-4d457942-17ae-4bb9-8315-ab4e05639542-478x598.jpg" alt="" width="478" height="598" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/on-display-the-tunisia-shirt-for-the-fifa-world-cup-2018-in-russia-picture-id962496684-story-large-4d457942-17ae-4bb9-8315-ab4e05639542-478x598.jpg 478w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/on-display-the-tunisia-shirt-for-the-fifa-world-cup-2018-in-russia-picture-id962496684-story-large-4d457942-17ae-4bb9-8315-ab4e05639542-922x1152.jpg 922w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/on-display-the-tunisia-shirt-for-the-fifa-world-cup-2018-in-russia-picture-id962496684-story-large-4d457942-17ae-4bb9-8315-ab4e05639542-446x557.jpg 446w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/on-display-the-tunisia-shirt-for-the-fifa-world-cup-2018-in-russia-picture-id962496684-story-large-4d457942-17ae-4bb9-8315-ab4e05639542-891x1114.jpg 891w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/on-display-the-tunisia-shirt-for-the-fifa-world-cup-2018-in-russia-picture-id962496684-story-large-4d457942-17ae-4bb9-8315-ab4e05639542-192x240.jpg 192w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/on-display-the-tunisia-shirt-for-the-fifa-world-cup-2018-in-russia-picture-id962496684-story-large-4d457942-17ae-4bb9-8315-ab4e05639542-384x480.jpg 384w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/on-display-the-tunisia-shirt-for-the-fifa-world-cup-2018-in-russia-picture-id962496684-story-large-4d457942-17ae-4bb9-8315-ab4e05639542-480x600.jpg 480w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/on-display-the-tunisia-shirt-for-the-fifa-world-cup-2018-in-russia-picture-id962496684-story-large-4d457942-17ae-4bb9-8315-ab4e05639542.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 478px) 100vw, 478px" /> Uhlsport tried to play it safe, carefully threw in a side detail but it doesn’t quite jazz up the look. The jersey doesn’t evoke strong emotions; in fact, you could fall asleep staring at the jersey. The jersey is quite reductive of the qualifier installment. 5.5/10 Egypt <img class="size-medium wp-image-658995 aligncenter lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/on-display-the-egypt-shirt-for-the-fifa-world-cup-2018-in-russia-picture-id962496592-story-large-f9a79d70-4d25-47a8-889f-85598a29b550-478x598.jpg" alt="" width="478" height="598" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/on-display-the-egypt-shirt-for-the-fifa-world-cup-2018-in-russia-picture-id962496592-story-large-f9a79d70-4d25-47a8-889f-85598a29b550-478x598.jpg 478w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/on-display-the-egypt-shirt-for-the-fifa-world-cup-2018-in-russia-picture-id962496592-story-large-f9a79d70-4d25-47a8-889f-85598a29b550-922x1152.jpg 922w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/on-display-the-egypt-shirt-for-the-fifa-world-cup-2018-in-russia-picture-id962496592-story-large-f9a79d70-4d25-47a8-889f-85598a29b550-446x557.jpg 446w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/on-display-the-egypt-shirt-for-the-fifa-world-cup-2018-in-russia-picture-id962496592-story-large-f9a79d70-4d25-47a8-889f-85598a29b550-891x1114.jpg 891w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/on-display-the-egypt-shirt-for-the-fifa-world-cup-2018-in-russia-picture-id962496592-story-large-f9a79